-- Burkhardt Says Blue Man Group Has `Global Visions' (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2012-08-21T13:32:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-21/burkhardt-says-blue-man-group-has-global-visions-audio-.html
Willy Burkhardt, president of Blue 
Man Productions, says the company's vision is to expand from a 
performing arts organization into an entertainment company with 
a global platform. Burkhardt talked to Bloomberg's  Kathleen Hays 
and Vonnie Quinn on "The Hays Advantage" on Bloomberg Radio on 
August 20, 2012.  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 17:01
 